---
<BlogLayout
  title="30 Essential Chinese Greetings Beyond 你好 (Nǐ Hǎo)"
  description="Go beyond 你好 with 30 practical Chinese greetings for every situation — formal, casual, phone, business, digital, and cultural contexts. Includes pronunciation, usage notes, and practice dialogues."
  language="chinese"
  category="chinese-basics"
  tags={["greetings", "beginner", "conversation", "phrases", "culture"]}
  publishDate="2026-02-19"
  image="https://images.pexels.com/photos/7653989/pexels-photo-7653989.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940"
  imageAlt="Two businessmen shaking hands in a modern office setting, symbolizing a successful business partnership."
  faq={faq}
  relatedTools={relatedTools}
